== TitanChat

TitanChat, a chat management plugin for Bukkit.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Features

* Edit settings in game with commands without editing config
* Create or delete channels
* Ban, unban, kick, mute or unmute players
* Admins, whitelists and blacklists for better administration
* Follow channels and receive their chat
* Use colour codes on channels
* Filter words
* Supports prefixes and suffixes
* All can be done with simple commands

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Functions

* Chat management
* Chat formating

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Dependecies

* CraftBukkit Build #1597

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== How to install

* Place in plugins folder
* Configure if you wish to
* Done!

